      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/1/10/5063",
      "text": [
        " اَلَّذِي يَقْذِفُ اِمْرَأَتَهُ قَالَ \"يُجْلَدُ\" قُلْتُ أَ رَأَيْتَ إِنْ عَفَتْ عَنْهُ قَالَ \"لاَ وَ لاَ كَرَامَةَ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.5063 - Al-Alaa narrated from Muhammad ibn Muslim from Abu Jafar Imam Muhammad ibn Ali Al-Baqir (as) regarding a man who accuses his wife (of adultery).\nImam (as) said: \"He is to be flogged.\"\nI asked: \"What if she pardons him?\"\nImam (as) said: \"No, and no honor (for him).\""
        ]
      }
    },
